00:12:37,390 --> 00:12:38,510
to report anything to him.

302
00:12:39,320 --> 00:12:40,790
Now, you're here in our court.

303
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,200
He can rest easy.

304
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:43,500
