447
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:01,980
Chun and I agreed

448
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:03,200
to give out some porridge.

449
00:18:03,310 --> 00:18:05,000
Our expenses will be

450
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,160
