451
00:18:06,270 --> 00:18:07,350
You should check it.

452
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:09,160
Giving out food is a worthy cause.

453
00:18:09,920 --> 00:18:11,350
Lan, you have my full support.

454
00:18:14,550 --> 00:18:15,510
We should go now.

455
00:18:25,590 --> 00:18:26,430
Found it.

